  <h2>Why Choose Ruby?</h2>
  <p>
    Ruby has long symbolized <em>love, courage, and protection</em>. Its fiery hue stands out against gold or platinum and reads well in both minimalist and ornate designs. As a member of the corundum family (like sapphire), ruby ranks <strong>9 on the Mohs scale</strong>, making it a strong choice for daily wear.
